features: 𝐋𝐨𝐨𝐤 𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐀𝐧𝐲𝐰𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐞: It has a super slim profile, foldable stand, 3 light modes, 2 ways to stand it up, removable 10X magnifier and rechargeable battery, this lighted makeup mirror is perfect for use in the travel, party, hotel, home and dressing table.

𝐇𝐞𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭 & 𝐀𝐧𝐠𝐥𝐞 𝐀𝐝𝐣𝐮𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐧𝐝: This compact mirror has 2 ways of standing, with a maximum standing height of 9 inches, and can also be folded from 0°-170°, while the mirror can stand stably at any angle as long as the bottom platform is on a flat surface. No crouching and bending over to do your makeup, it definitely makes doing makeup so much easier.

𝐒𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐥𝐥 𝐒𝐞𝐧𝐬𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐜𝐡: This desk mirror equipped with an advanced angle sensor switch, the mirror light automatically turns on when you open it up and shuts down when you fold it closed, just like a laptop, it will automatically turn on and off to save power.

𝐒𝐥𝐢𝐦 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭 𝐃𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐠𝐧: Size: 5.1in*7.5in. It’s about the size of an iPad mini or small tablet and you can easily put it into a medium size purse/bag/the included travel pouch, and the small mirror has anti-slip pads on the bottom 4 corners to prevent it from slipping around Slide on a flat surface. When not in use, The compact and foldable design makes the mirror and lights protected from any possible damage.

𝐑𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝟏𝟎𝐗 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐧𝐢𝐟𝐲𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐌𝐢𝐫𝐫𝐨𝐫: This led mirror set comes with a 1X HD mirror and a 10X magnifying mirror. The 10X removable magnifier with vacuum suction cup on the back, so you can attach and detach as you need, also can be placed anywhere on the mirror. 𝐍𝐎𝐓𝐄: The 10X magnifying mirror is recommended to be used within 4 inches of distance, is of great quality and won't give you that weird warped upside down affect.

𝟑 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭 𝐌𝐨𝐝𝐞𝐬 & 𝐒𝐭𝐞𝐩𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐃𝐢𝐦𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐠: The Alovely light up mirror offers 3 colors of lighting: with warm, natural and cool settings, you can adjust the lighting to match any environment or occasion. Through stepless dimming, the mirror's brightness can be continuously adjusted to meet your needs, and it also has an intelligent memory function that retains the brightness and color temperature of the last used light for easy use next time, saves the trouble of frequent adjustments.

𝐂𝐨𝐫𝐝𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝟏𝟐𝟎𝟎𝐦𝐀𝐡 𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐠𝐞𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐁𝐚𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐲: Built-in 1200mAh rechargeable lithium battery, wireless use, Type-C charging, battery life up to 8 hours, also has a 15-minute scheduled shutdown function, which effectively saves energy and does not require frequent charging, easily meeting your makeup needs.

𝐈𝐝𝐞𝐚𝐥 𝐆𝐢𝐟𝐭 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐇𝐞𝐫: Whether it’s birthday, anniversary, Mother’s Day, Thanksgiving, Christmas, or any holiday, the vanity mirror with lights makes for a thoughtful and practical gift that any beauty enthusiast will appreciate. Its versatile features and stylish design make it an ideal gift for makeup lovers, travelers, or anyone who wants to look their best.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A great vanity mirror, perfect for beauty needs!
reviews.reviewText: I just moved into my new home, which was a new build, and while I love my home, the lighting and the setup in the bathrooms aren't 100% to my liking. The mirrors are too far away from the sink and the lighting is a bit dim. This mirror is a lifesaver and solved my problems! It lets me get close to see my skin and my pores and examine my eyebrows for tweezing and any problem areas on my skin that need to be addressed.The larger portion of the mirror itself is great. It has three lighting settings, so you can decide which lighting scheme (soft glow, bright glow, etc.) works best for you. It's very easy to toggle between the three settings with just a button tap which is right on the unit. The smaller, magnifying mirror that suctions to the main mirror really magnifies the areas you want to see. You can really see up close to get those few pesky stray eyebrows plucked or to do a nice liner of the eye if you'd like. And the suction is very strong and stable. It doesn't fall off the mirror at all.The mirror came in a cute little drawstring bag and the mirror folds up flat, so it's neat and tidy. Everything (the mirror, the suctioned magnifying mirror, and the charging cable) fits in the bag so you can take the whole thing with you when you travel. You can easily carry it in a backpack if you'd like, or a purse if the purse is large enough. The mirror comes with a charging cable (no charging unit itself, but I just plugged it into an empty computer port or you can use a phone charger) and it charged extremely fast. The battery life is also great. I don't think I'll have to charge this mirror for a long time.If you're looking for a lightweight and portable, yet powerful, lighted vanity mirror, you won't go wrong with this one. The first time I used it, my husband said, "Um, can you order me one of those for my bathroom, too?" so I guess I'll be purchasing a second one. I'll probably get one for my mother for Christmas, too. She loves to sit on her bed and do her makeup, so this will be a miracle for her!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for travel
reviews.reviewText: Ordered to take on trips when traveling. Compact, easy to operate, neat storage bag, and it actually works. The light works and able to brighten or dim. Great for use away for home or away. Wish the magnifying mirror was a little bigger, but overall great product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is so handy with traveling-it’s light and compact! I didn’t realize it came with a light as well so that was a bonus!! The light is bright and the mirror slides out to create its own stand. I’m getting a little older so my eyesight is not as good, so I got it for the magnifying mirror. It was a little smaller than I thought but it still gets the job done :) IIt all comes in a handy bag so you can keep the charging cord with it. I recommend this highly!
